    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna fazzija: Laid ta-\nwa Kalpone Schehlaſtibu atrohd\ntawas Azziß:tad nogahje ta See-\nwa fawu Zektu/ un ehde/ un win-\nras Waigs ne raudſijahs wairs\ntik noskummiß.\n"
