    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz kahdu Laſku tappe\nAnna gruhta/un dſeindeja weenu\nDehlu/ un nofanze winna Wahr-\nduSamuels/jo (fazzija winna)/\nes efinu to no ta KUNGGA iſlub-\nguſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu taß Wihrß Elka-\nnus ar wiſſu fawuNammu gahje/\ntam KUNGAM uppureht to\ngadskahrtigu Uppuri/ un fawu\nApfohlſchanu/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad ne gahje Anna lihds/\nbet fazzija us fawu Wibru : Kad\nto wiſſis atſchſirts tohr / tad\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
