    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Elkanus winnasWihr\nfazzijaus to : darri/ kaſtew lab\npatihk/ paleez teitan/ teekams\nwinnu buhſi atſchkihrufi/bet ta\nKUNGGA laid apſtiprina fan\nWahrdn. Ta palikke ta Seewu\nun ſihdinaja fawuDehlu/teekams\nwinna to atſchkihre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz kad winna to btj a\nſchkiruſi / wedde winna to lihi\nar ſewim uß augſchu / ar tri\nWehrſcheem/un weenuEepuMi\ntu/ un weenu Trauzinu ar Wil\nnu / un ta wedde winnu eekſch ta\nKUNGGA Nammu uß Sihlu/u\ntas Puutis bija wehl jauns.\n"
