      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta fazzija : Ak man\nKungs ! tik teefcham ka taw\nDwehfele dſihwo / mans Kungs\neß efinu taSeewa/kas fcheitan pe\ntewis ſtahweja to KUNGGA luhg\ndana.\n"
    },
